<br>
So the next questions are: How can FT go about helping to guard our new found toy AND how do we prevent Hib/Mid rogues from doing the same thing to Albion?<br>
<br>
Any suggestions?<br>
<br>
Anyone willing to sacrifice a lowbie character slot to move to the relic keep and log in to check the keep doors once in a while?<br>
<br>
Anyone have someone with a little woodworking skill that we could load up with boards for repair tasks? <br>
<br>
I'm not sure how this works, but it sounds like we now have two relics at our keep. Ours and the Hibs. It seems like that relic keep will be a prime target for the Hibs, but it might be especially tempting for the Mids, who could take two relics with one raid...<br>
